{"word":"ἐπαιωρέω","slug":"ἐπαιωρέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαιωρέω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ήσω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to keep hovering over, keep in suspense</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to hover over, to buoy up</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to overhang, threaten</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}